    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the ability to infect a humanoid's mind with the alien magic of your patron. You can take a Magic action to touch an &amp;Reference[incapacitated] humanoid. That creature is awakened from its incapacitated state and is &amp;Reference[charmed] by you until a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplRemoveCurs]{Remove Curse} spell is cast on it, the Charmed condition is removed from it, or you use this feature again. If the Charmed condition is removed you instantaneously know.</p><p>You can communicate telepathically with the Charmed creature as long as the two of you are on the same plane of existence.</p>",
